{"tid":1444004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【有圖】岩岩去完北角","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:04:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:20:49.000Z","uid":122994,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"938e084807130319d502717cdcd5fd9158e54d1e","tid":1444004,"uid":122994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:04:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩食飯路過，真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成條街咁多人想搵個講廣東話都無。基本上得d福健佬，黑警同記者，少量途人係度睇熱鬧。而d黑警亦係d支那樣既生物<br />\n<br />\n去到果時d福健佬已經失曬控，不斷指鬧記者，繼而動武。黑警就好似護住果班人咁四圍巡遊咁。<br />\n<br />\n一大條繁簡錯譯既banner掛係橋上。好明顯佢地既策略就係等人拉示威者過黎，然後開大片，之後黑警拉示威者放福健佬。點知真係無人去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位手足真係唔洗去北角，今晚讓子彈飛，班fucking佬繼續失控，分分鐘同警犬開片。呢個係記者既回合<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D2C3J91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD2C3J91.jpg&h=de966e48&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6fbae4870d1c13054c28c45bf3701d632d3f816","tid":1444004,"uid":54248,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:04:31.000Z","msg":"咪撚去"},{"pid":"ac3bf1278b51ccb37296a44438d051c841dca593","tid":1444004,"uid":266010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"721 今日唔撚去北角"},{"pid":"bac461a8f0b41fc4cefece9fe78265bd0890e302","tid":1444004,"uid":241628,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:04:59.000Z","msg":"我地唔係要撚班福獨<br />\n而係支持佢<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">白拎維穩費進行福獨</span></span></strong><br />\n呢招叫 以子之矛攻子之盾"},{"pid":"2c4248229b8902bbf1fb1c53a83bf4b0463cb773","tid":1444004,"uid":67303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"推呀 各位手捉唔好去呀"},{"pid":"83eb90a3865db1a62bcccbeab2ccf0a5d435ee97","tid":1444004,"uid":67303,"like":0,"dislike":0,